defaultmovement
default as a founder member of the Community Energy Coalition 
defaultwhich includes national organisations with a combined membership of 15 million such as The National Trust and The Church of England. It campaigns to enable communities to own, generate and save energy for the benefit of all.
defaultPure Leapfrog has built a loan portfolio of close to 20 community energy projects, primarily using solar PV, but also biomass boilers, LEDs and solar thermal.
